Package: HealthyDietDashboard
Type: Shiny
Title: Global Cost of a Healthy Diet (R Shiny Dashboard)
Version: 1.0.0
Description: An R Shiny dashboard for exploring the cost of a healthy diet
    across countries and regions from 2017 to 2022, using FAO and World Bank data.
Authors@R: person("Hooman", "Esteki", role = c("aut", "cre"))
